narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Learning pedagogical knowledge and practising it in our own classes has contributed to my development enormously. The feedback I received for every single assignment was constructive and very useful.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: It's a very well designed course with lots of opportunities to practice and reflect your own teaching. A wide range of activities and interesting topics are included in the syllabus. The professor is incredibly helpful and simply wonderful. It was a unique opportunity for me to take her course.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would definitely recommend this course to those who would like to build upon their existing pedagogical knowledge and practice teaching skills without being constrained by old school assignments.
